      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; white-space: normal;\"><div><span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">如果你想要学习</span><a href=\"http://lib.csdn.net/base/linux\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 52, 52); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; font-weight: bold;\" title=\"Linux知识库\">Linux</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">或者经常使用</span><a href=\"http://lib.csdn.net/base/linux\" style=\"color: rgb(223, 52, 52); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; font-weight: bold;\" title=\"Linux知识库\">linux</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">，那么熟练掌握一种编辑器是十分有必要的。我一直使用的是vi，虽然有点繁琐，但提供的功能真心强大，熟练掌握后必将受益无穷。下面分享一下我的学习心得。</span></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想试试vim的话，</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">类Unix机器可以键入：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">vimtutor</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">windows机器可以键入：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">:help tutor</span></div><div><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px; border: none; white-space: pre-wrap; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">一、进入vi</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">虽然只是打开一个文件都有学问，掌握好能快速帮你定位到想要的位置，如下：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi filename :打开或新建文件，并将光标置于第一行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi +n filename ：打开文件，并将光标置于第n行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi + filename ：打开文件，并将光标置于最后一行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi +/pattern filename：打开文件，并将光标置于第一个与pattern匹配的串处</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi -r filename ：在上次正用vi编辑时发生系统崩溃，恢复filename</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">vi filename....filename ：打开多个文件，依次进行编辑</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">二、光标移动</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">这个是vi的基础，我们平时的工作会经常要编辑文本或查找日志信息，所以上一页下一页上一行下一行神马的用的非常频繁，下面就罗列一下关于一定光标的相关指令。</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">1.上下左右：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">h：左移一个字符</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">j：下移一行</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">k：上移一行</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">l：右移一字符</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">2.行内移动</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">0：所在行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">$：所在行行尾</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">^：所在行首字母</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">3.屏幕内移动</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">H：当前屏幕首行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">M：当前屏幕中间行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">L：当前屏幕尾行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">4.移动指定行</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">n-：上移n行至行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">n+：下移n行至行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">n$：下移n-1行至行尾</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">5.移动到特定位置</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">G：移至最后一行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">nG：移至第n行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">gg：移至第一行行首</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">三、翻页</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">翻页命令对于我们查找日志信息非常有帮助，如下：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em;\"><div>Ctrl+u：向文件首翻半屏&nbsp;</div><div>Ctrl+d：向文件尾翻半屏&nbsp;</div><div>Ctrl+f：向文件尾翻一屏&nbsp;</div><div>Ctrl＋b；向文件首翻一屏&nbsp;</div><div style=\"-en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"-en-paragraph: true;\">nz：将第n行滚至屏幕顶部，不指定n时将当前行滚至屏幕顶部，输入完敲回车。</span></div></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">四、编辑文本</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">如果你仅仅是要查看文件内容，可用view等其他命令，我们经常会用vi来编辑文本。虽然有点繁琐但非常实用，需要好好掌握，如下：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">1.删除文本</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">x：删除光标所在位置的字符</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">dw：删除光标所在位置的单词（应该是从当前字符开始到下个单词结束）</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">dd：删除光标所在行</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">d$：删除光标所在位置到行尾的内容</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">2.复制和粘贴</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">y可用来赋值文本，结合其他命令，可以实现：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">yd：复制单词</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">y$：复制到行尾</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">p用来粘贴文本，要实现剪切：使用d删除命令，然后用p将刚删除的内容粘贴到想要的位置。如果要赋值大段的内容，用上面的方法比较麻烦，可用v命令：在要复制的内容开始出按下v，移动光标到结束位置（移动命令参照上面），文本会高亮显示，按下y赋值选中的内容，再用p将文本粘贴到想要的位置即可。</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">五、查找</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">我们会经常要根据关键字查找日志信息，比如用户名、账号等，查找命令很简单，有如下两种：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">1.从光标处往后搜索</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">/pattern：pattern即为要搜索的关键字，如果后面有即定位到第一次出现的位置，如果没有则从文本开始处搜索知道找到匹配出。用n可继续定位下一个出现的位置（向后搜索）。</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">2.从光标处往前搜索</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">?pattern：pattern即为要搜索的关键字，如果前面没有就从文本末尾开始搜索。用n可继续定位下一个出现的位置（向前搜索）。</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">六、替换</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">使用替换命令可将某些特定的内容替换其他的内容，如下：</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:s/old/new/ 替换当前行第一个 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:s/old/new/g 替换当前行所有 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:m,ns/old/new/ 替换m到n行第一个 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:m,ns/old/new/g 替换m到n行所有 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:m,$s/old/new/ 替换第m行到尾行第一个 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:m,$s/old/new/g 替换第m行到尾行所有 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:%s/old/new/ 替换整个文本每行第一个 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:%s/old/new/g 替换整个文本所有 old 为 new</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -en-paragraph: true;\">:%s/old/new/gc 替换整个文本所有 old 为 new ，每次出现提示</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">以上就是比较常用的vi命令，也是我平时用的比较多的，如果错误欢迎指正。</span></div><div><br/></div></div>"
    }
  ]
}